      • getStatus

        public LicenseStatus getStatus()
        Gets the status of the license

        The status can be one of the following:

        • LicenseStatus.VALID
        • LicenseStatus.EXPIRED
        • LicenseStatus.INVALID
        • LicenseStatus.MAX_USES_REACHED
        Returns:
        the status of the license
